i will be install terraform from the HashiCorp official method 

Firstly Add the HashiCorp GPG Key 

curl -fsSL https://apt.releases.hashicorp.com/gpg | sudo gpg --dearmor -o /usr/share/keyrings/hashicorp-archive-keyring.gpg

Secondly Add HashiCorp repository 

echo "deb [signed-by=/usr/share/keyrings/hashicorp-archive-keyring.gpg] https://apt.releases.hashicorp.com $(lsb_release -cs) main" | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/hashicorp.list

Step 3

Install terraform 

sudo apt update && sudo apt install terraform -y

Step 4 Verify 

terraform version 

Terraform v1.x.x

After Terraform Installed 

You need to install Helm (Kubernetes Package Manager)

Step 1: Download Helm install script 

curl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/helm/helm/main/scripts/get-helm-3 | bash

Step 2: Verify 

helm version 

Expected Result 

version.BuildInfo{Version:"v3.x.x"}

